The sensitivity of the detecting system was evaluated by investigating the effect of different MTs concentrations on the CQD–AuNP system fluorescence intensity under the optimum conditions mentioned above. Notably, the fluorescence emission of the CQD–AuNP system recovered gradually with increasing MTs concentration (Fig. 8
                        A). Fig. 8B shows that the fluorescence recovery efficiency [(F–F

