                           0
                         = 0.00432cMTs (nmol L−1) - 0.0144, and the data fitting shows the correlation coefficient of 0.9951. The limit of detection (LOD) was found to be 5.25 nmol L−1. The relative standard deviation of repeated measurement of 9.4 × 10−8 mol L−1 MTs was 2.9%.
